9:36Z"}, "body": "\r\n## Motivation\r\n\r\nPreviously in order for the consumer to\r\nregister interest, in a notification triggered by\r\n`notify_waiters`, the `Notified` future had to be\r\npolled. This introduced friction when using the api\r\nas the future had to be pinned before polled.\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\n\r\nThis change introduces a counter that tracks how many\r\ntimes `notified_waiters` has been called. Upon creation of\r\nthe future the number of times is loaded. When first\r\npolled the future compares this number with the count\r\nstate of the `Notify` type. This avoids the need for\r\nregistering the waiter upfront.\r\n\r\n\r\nFixes: #3066\r\n\r\nSigned-off-by: Zahari Dichev <zaharidichev@gmail.com>\r\n", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/tokio-rs/tokio/issues/3098/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/tokio-rs/tokio/issues/3098/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null, "score": 1.0}, {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/tokio-rs/tokio/issues/2743", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/tokio-rs/tokio", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/tokio-rs/tokio/issues/2743/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/tokio-rs/tokio/issues/2743/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/tokio-rs/tokio/issues/2743/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/tokio-rs/tokio/pull/2743", "id": 674807182, "node_id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDY0NDMwODI4", "number": 2743, "title": "net: restore TcpStream::{poll_read_ready, poll_write_ready}", "user": {"login": "masnagam", "id": 2015132, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjIwMTUxMzI=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2015132?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/masnagam", "html_url": "https://github.com/masnagam", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/masnagam/fol